      <title>重新安装windows无法选择版本的问题</title>
      <link>https://syaofox.github.io/windows/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85windows%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link>
